      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Behdseet no Babeles Wid-\ndus/ un eita ahra no to Kalde-\neru Semmes/ un tohpeet kà\nAbschi ta gannama Pulka\nPreekschd."
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo rangi/ Es uhszelschu\nleelu Tauto Pulku no tahs\nSemmes prett Seemeka-Pusti/\nun weddischu to prett Babeli/\ntee taitisees prett winnu / no\ntennenes taps winna usneinta/\nwixxa Bultas buhs kà kahda fa-\nprattiga Warrena/ neiveena at-\ngreestees tukfcha."
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un to Kaldeëru Semme\nbuhs par Laupijumu/ wiſſi/ kas\nto aplaupa / taps pee-ehdinati/\nfakka tas KUNGS."
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tapehz ka juhs preeza-\ntees/ un no Preeka vslezzat/ juhs\nPohstitajt mannas eemantoja-\nmas Teefas/ jo juhs effat weh-\nligi tappufschi/ kà wehligs Tetſch/\nun sweedsat kà tee stipri Sirgi."
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Juhsfo Mahte irr kohti\navkaunota/ kas juhs irr dsem-\ndejsi irr Kannà tappufs/ reds/ to\nPagazu Galß irr tuksch/ kaltis/\nun klaissch."
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta KUNGA Dusmibas\nDeht winna ne taps eedshwota/\nbet taps wisshnotak pohstá/ wiſſ/\nkas Babelet fezzen eet/ brihni-\ntees/ un fwilpehs pahr winnas\nMohkahm."
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Taitajtees prett Babeli\napkahrt/ wiſſi/ kas to Stohpu\nuswekt/schanjeet eeksch winnas/"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "ne tauajt tahs Bultas/ jota irr\nprett to KUNGU grehkojſi."
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Gawilejeet pahr winnu\nwiszapkahrt/ winnat irr Rohkà\njadohdas/ winnas Pamatti irr\nkrittusch/ winnas Muhei irr no-\nlansiti.\nJo ta irr ta KUNGA"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Atreepschana/ atreebjeetees prett\nwinnu/ itt kà winna irr darrij-\nfi/ ta darrajt winnai."
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Israujeet no Babeles tik\nlabbi to Gehjeju/ kà to / kas to\nZirpi walka pfaujamá Laiká/\nlaid ikweens preeffch ta breefin-\nga Sohbina greeschahs pee teem\nLandim/ un behg ikkatrs uhs ja-\nwu Semmi."
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Israëls irr weens istai-\nshts gannams Pulks / ko tee\nLauwas irr istrenkajtchi.\nTas\npirmajs/ kas winnu irr apehdís/\nbija tas Kehninsch no Affirijas/\nun ichis tas pehdigajs Nebukad-\nRezars tas Kehninsch no Babe-\nles/ irr winna Kaulus fatreezis."
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tadeht ta fakka tas\nKUNGS Zebaot/ tas Israëta\nDeews: Reds/ Es peemekefschu\nto Kehuihu no Babeles/ un win-\nna Semmi/ itt kà es etmu pee-\nmekejs to Kehnizu no Affirijas."
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un weddischu Israëlu at-\nek fawa Mahjas-Weeta / un\ntas gannitees us Karmelu/ un\nBahsanu / un winna Dwehfele\ntaps us teem Gèwräima un Gi-\nleudas Kalneem pee-ehdinata."
    }
  ],
